Sajal Chowdhury is a List A cricketer from Bangladesh. He was born on 23 March 1978 in Bramin Baria and is a right-handed batsman and right arm medium fast bowler. He played 7 one day matches for Chittagong Division in 2000/01 and also represented the Bangladesh under 19 side in 6 youth one day internationals. He represented Bangladesh in 4 List A matches in the SAARC Quadrangular tournament in 1994/95 before they attained test status. His best list A bowling, 2 for 27, came against Dhaka Division. 
